==== Simple Example: show the Help:Start page upon extending ====

<source>
{{#widget: com.fluidops.iwb.widget.CollapsibleWidget | 
 appearance = 
   {{ expandedLabel = 'Close Help:Start'
    | isExpanded = false
    | collapsedLabel = 'Open Help:Start'
   }}
 | pageUri = 'Help:Start'
}}
</source>